  "system": {
    "description": {
      "value": "<p>At 7th level, your auditory commands physically moves others.</p><p>As an action you may spend 4 Cursed Energy and target one creature within 10 feet of you.</p><p>This creature must make a strength saving throw vs your genjutsu Save DC.</p><p>On a failed save, they're knocked back up to 90 feet.</p><p>If the creature collides with a surface they take double falling damage.</p><p>Alternatively, when you cast a genjutsu you may spend 3 Cursed Energy.</p><p>If affected creatures fail the save, they're immediately knocked prone and knocked back 45 feet.</p><p>When Magnified: You may target any number creature within 30 feet of you.</p><p></p>",
